extends ./layouts/layout.jade

block content
  .row
    .col-xs-12.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
      .jumbotron
        h3.text-center How to Play
        hr
        ul
          li
            h4 Pick one winner per day.
          li  
            h4 Pick each team no more than once per month.
          li
            h4 Predictions can be changed or cancelled at any point up until a game's scheduled start time.
          li
            h4 Players are not required to choose a team every day.
          li
            h4 Players are ranked solely on the number of their successful predictions. 
              small For example, a player with a 6-3 record would be ranked
                em &nbsp;ahead
                | &nbsp;of a 5-0 player.
          li
            h4 All predictions become public as soon as the game begins. 
              small (They appear on the Standings page.)
        hr
        p Let me know if you can think of any other scenarios that are worth codifying in the rules.
